{
  "message": "test(conformance): add FFT and Signal metamorphic cases (+24)\n\nFFT metamorphic (12 cases):\n- fft_ifft_inverse: inverse identity property\n- fft_linearity: linear combination preservation\n- fft_parseval: energy preservation theorem\n- fftshift_ifftshift_inverse: shift round-trip\n- rfft_hermitian_symmetry: real input symmetry\n- fft2/fftn inverse variants for 2D/3D\n\nSignal metamorphic (12 cases):\n- convolve_commutative: order independence\n- convolve_identity: delta kernel identity\n- convolve_distributive: distribution over addition\n- convolve_scaling: scalar factor propagation\n- correlate autocorrelation properties (peak, symmetry)\n- correlate_time_reversal: reversal relationship\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
